===================================================================
 Generate a list of 100 random integers and count the even values.
===================================================================

list-of-numbers : apply [random 1000] 100 times

"There are ", even values in (list-of-numbers), " even values in the list." â†²

even values in (the-list) :
	even : 0
	for each (item) in (the-list) do
		if ((item) is divisible by 2)
			(even) ++
	return even